## Modelos de Datos (18 models)

| Model | Fields clave |
|-------|-------------|
| **User** | email, passwordHash (select:false), roleId, profile (firstName, lastName, licenseNumber, phone), isActive, lastLoginAt |
| **RefreshToken** | token (unique), userId, expiresAt (TTL), revokedAt, replacedBy, createdByIp |
| **Tenant** | tenantId (uuid), ownerUserId, status, plan, trialEndsAt, country (code, currency, timezone) |
| **Role** | name, permissions[], isSystem, auditTrail[] |
| **Permission** | code, category, description |
| **Patient** | personalInfo (firstName, lastName, dni, birthDate, gender, phone, email, address), emergencyContact, status, insuranceInfo, generalObservations |
| **ClinicalEntry** | patientId, professionalId, date, type (session/evaluation/note), content (structured), privateNotes |
| **Appointment** | patientId, professionalId, startTime, endTime, duration, type, modality (in_person/online), status, meetingUrl, isRecurring |
| **Schedule** | professionalId, dayOfWeek, startTime, endTime, slotDuration, blockedSlots[], vacations[] |
| **Payment** | patientId, amount, currency, method (cash/transfer/card/insurance), status, receiptNumber, insuranceCoverage |
| **Subscription** | plan, status, currentPeriod, pricing, paymentHistory[], externalSubscriptionId |
| **Invoice** | invoiceNumber, amount, currency, status, issuedAt, dueDate, paidAt |
| **Branding** | nombrePublico, logo, colors, nombreDelBot, tonoDelBot |
| **ConsentTemplate** | title, content, version, isActive |
| **ConsentDocument** | patientId, templateId, signedAt, signatureType |
| **Attachment** | patientId, filename, mimeType, size, path/url |
| **TenantMetrics** | period (year/month), patients stats, appointments stats, financial stats, bot stats |
| **BotAuditLog** | sessionId, userPhone, messageContent, botResponse, governanceAction, latencyMs |

**Plugins de Mongoose:**
- `tenantPlugin` → agrega `tenantId` field + auto-filter en queries
- `softDeletePlugin` → `isDeleted`, `deletedAt`, [softDelete()](file:///c:/Users/Benicio/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/psicosaas/src/modules/patient/patient.service.ts#54-59) method
- `auditPlugin` → `createdBy`, `updatedBy`, `createdAt`, `updatedAt`

---

## Seguridad implementada

- ✅ JWT con rotación de refresh tokens (detección de reuso)
- ✅ Passwords hasheados con bcrypt (12 rounds)
- ✅ RBAC granular con 33 permisos
- ✅ Aislamiento multi-tenant por query
- ✅ Helmet (HTTP security headers)
- ✅ CORS configurable
- ✅ Rate limiting (global + auth-specific)
- ✅ Validación con Zod en todos los endpoints
- ✅ Error handler centralizado (no leak de info en production)
- ✅ `passwordHash` excluido de queries por defecto
- ✅ Graceful shutdown

---

## Características técnicas relevantes para el frontend

1. **Autenticación**: Bearer token en header `Authorization`. Access token de 15 min, refresh automático
2. **Paginación**: Cursor-based (`?cursor=<ObjectId>&limit=20`), respuesta `{ data, pagination: { nextCursor, hasMore } }`
3. **Errores**: Formato consistente `{ status: 'error', code: 'CODE', message: '...' }`
4. **IDs**: MongoDB ObjectIds (`507f1f77bcf86cd799439011`)
5. **Fechas**: ISO 8601 strings
6. **Moneda**: ARS por defecto, precios en centavos (ej: 4999 = $49,99)
7. **Estado del tenant**: trial → active → suspended → cancelled
8. **Real-time**: No hay WebSockets implementados (polling sería necesario para notificaciones)
9. **File uploads**: Multipart form-data, almacenamiento local (preparado para S3)
10. **CORS**: Configurable via `CORS_ORIGIN` env var

---

## Lo que NO tiene el backend (gaps para MVP)

- ❌ WebSockets / real-time events
- ❌ Email sending (módulo de notificaciones existe como scaffold pero no envía)
- ❌ API documentation (Swagger/OpenAPI)
- ❌ Containerización (Docker)
- ❌ CI/CD pipeline
- ❌ Frontend
